{"name":"Barbarian","type":"class","img":"systems/pergasha-foundryvtt/icons/skills/weapon_01.jpg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>As a barbarian, you gain the following class features.</p>\n<h3>Hit Points</h3>\n<p><strong>Hit Dice:</strong> 1d12 per barbarian level<br /><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level:</strong> 12 + your Constitution modifier<br /><strong>Hit Points at Higher Levels:</strong> 1d12 (or 7) + your Constitution modifier per barbarian level after 1st</p>\n<h3>Proficiencies</h3>\n<p><strong>Armor:</strong> Light armor, medium armor, shields<br /><strong>Weapons:</strong> Simple weapons, martial weapons<br /><strong>Saving Throws:</strong> Choose one physical score (Strength, Dexterity, Constitution) and one mental score (Wisdom, Intelligence, Charisma). You have proficiency in saving throws for these two abilities.<br /><strong>Skills and Tools:</strong> Choose any two skills or tools.</p>\n<h1>Barbarian Advancement</h1>\n<table style=\"width:98.9547%\" border=\"0\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:5.6338%\">Level</td>\n<td style=\"width:11.9718%\">Proficiency Bonus</td>\n<td style=\"width:61.9718%\">Features</td>\n<td style=\"width:10.3873%\">Rages</td>\n<td style=\"width:8.62676%\">Rage Damage</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:5.6338%\">1st</td>\n<td style=\"width:11.9718%\">+2</td>\n<td style=\"width:61.9718%\">@Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.Wt9JY5lX5kMOI6oY]{Rage}, @Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.yxBxcrphuLAS72NZ]{Unarmored Defense (Barbarian)}</td>\n<td style=\"width:10.3873%\">2</td>\n<td style=\"width:8.62676%\">+2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:5.6338%\">2nd</td>\n<td style=\"width:11.9718%\">+2</td>\n<td style=\"width:61.9718%\">@Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.wKwhEnf461xbm19f]{Danger Sense}, @Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.SyTarkNv3I8P1672]{Naturalist},@Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.iK149jUJCG1K3seU]{Reckless Attack}</td>\n<td style=\"wi