+4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:5.6338%\">17th</td>\n<td style=\"width:11.9718%\">+6</td>\n<td style=\"width:61.9718%\">@Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.g3QVc70F7d8J44cw]{Brutal Critical}(3 dice)</td>\n<td style=\"width:10.3873%\">6</td>\n<td style=\"width:8.62676%\">+4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:5.6338%\">18th</td>\n<td style=\"width:11.9718%\">+6</td>\n<td style=\"width:61.9718%\">@Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.kdKRhL558qjKnPXz]{Indomitable Might}</td>\n<td style=\"width:10.3873%\">6</td>\n<td style=\"width:8.62676%\">+4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:5.6338%\">19th</td>\n<td style=\"width:11.9718%\">+6</td>\n<td style=\"width:61.9718%\">@Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.jfiYMZgi2xCgbXOW]{Ability Score Improvement}</td>\n<td style=\"width:10.3873%\">6</td>\n<td style=\"width:8.62676%\">+4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:5.6338%\">20th</td>\n<td style=\"width:11.9718%\">+6</td>\n<td style=\"width:61.9718%\">@Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.FvVwCoVivBv9MXhP]{Primal Champion}</td>\n<td style=\"width:10.3873%\">Unlimited</td>\n<td style=\"width:8.62676%\">+4</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h1>Primal Paths</h1>\n<h2>Path of the Ancestral Guardian</h2>\n<p>Some barbarians hail from cultures that revere their ancestors. These tribes teach that the warriors of the past linger in the world as mighty spirits, who can guide and protect the living. When a barbarian who follows this path rages, the barbarian contacts the spirit world and calls on these guardian spirits for aid.</p>\n<p>Barbarians who draw on their ancestral guardians can better fight to protect their tribes and their allies. To cement ties to their ancestral guardians, barbarians who follow this path cover themselves in elaborate tattoos that celebrate their ancestors' deeds. These tattoos tell sagas of victories against terrible monsters and other fearsome rivals.</p>\n<h3>Path of the Ancestral Guardian Features</h3>\n<p>3rd Level: @Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.SyTDdGt7xsh3vITW]{Ancestral Protectors}</p>\n<p>6th Level: @Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.DTQTFB1VwNQQ3i9C]{Spirit Shield}</p>\n<p>10th Level: @Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.zJiBwSZMNSvGZ1RY]{Guided by the Spirits}</p>\n<p>14th Level: @Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.F2yEXtO6gS91FcBk]{Vengeful Ancestors}</p>\n<h2>Path of the Beast</h2>\n<p>Barbarians who walk the Path of Beast draw their rage from a bestial spark burning within their souls. That beast howls to be released and bursts forth in the throes of rage.</p>\n<p>Those who tread this path might be inhabited by a primal spirit or descended from shapeshifters. You can choose the origin of your feral might or determine it randomly by rolling on the following table.</p>\n<table style=\"width:98.9547%;height:97px\" border=\"1\">\n<thead>\n<tr style=\"height:16px\">\n<td style=\"width:6.37375%;height:16px\"><strong>d4</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width:92.746%;height:16px\"><strong>Origin</strong></td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height:16px\">\n<td style=\"width:6.37375%;height:16px\">1</td>\n<td style=\"width:92.746%;height:16px\">A Sundering Storm tainted you with twisted bestial abilities and characteristics</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:33px\">\n<td style=\"width:6.37375%;height:33px\">2</td>\n<td style=\"width:92.746%;height:33px\">You are descended from a legendary druid who lived before the Sundering, and this ancestor's powers flow through your veins</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:16px\">\n<td style=\"width:6.37375%;height:16px\">3</td>\n<td style=\"width:92.746%;height:16px\">An ancestral spirit gifted you with the ability to adopt different bestial aspects</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:16px\">\n<td style=\"width:6.37375%;height:16px\">4</td>\n<td style=\"width:92.746%;height:16px\">An ancient animal spirit dwells within you, allowing you to walk this path</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3>Path of the Beast Features</h3>\n<p>3rd Level: @Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.Cql36lDfb7ZGIzVl]{Form of the Beast}</p>\n<p>6th Level: @Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.4BmpAtw79sndY23G]{Bestial Soul}</p>\n<p>10th Level: @Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.N2H5kxrEl69y80Jp]{Infectious Fury}</p>\n<p>14th Level: @Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.RPiX43lXgi7sa5st]{Call the Hunt}</p>\n<h2>Path of the Primal Warrior</h2>\n<p>The primal warrior hails from the remote and most sundered regions of the world where monstrous aberrations are common. Your fury is truly primal, and your methods unrefined, but you may stand tall atop the primordial food chain among the strongest creatures ever to have lived.</p>\n<h3>Path of the Primal Warrior Features</h3>\n<p>3rd Level: @Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.ZvUYBUtIoUDUjK7V]{Brutal Attack}, @Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.dm3FFEchFlYbgFT7]{Brutality}, @Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.e3V4SIhBpNApXYiz]{Brutalities}</p>\n<p>6th Level: @Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.WSIE9bAVocZMwold]{Animal Instincts}</p>\n<p>10th Level: @Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.uNgFnnnLjSgJEuaq]{Robust Constitution}</p>\n<p>14th Level: @Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.vW6yKwrU5pvGVBWn]{Colossal Weapon Master}</p>\n<h2>Path of the Totem Warrior</h2>\n<p>The Path of the Totem Warrior is a spiritual journey, as the barbarian accepts a spirit animal as guide, protector, and inspiration. In battle, your totem spirit fills you with supernatural might, adding ancestral fuel to your barbarian rage.</p>\n<p>Most barbarian tribes consider a totem animal to be kin to a particular clan. In such cases, it is unusual for an individual to have more than one totem animal spirit, though exceptions exist.</p>\n<h3>Path of the Totem Warrior Features</h3>\n<p>3rd Level: @Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.vdnnVyLnK4tNY7Jg]{Spirit Seeker}, @Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.dp4L8SA3Y39DyMjF]{Totem Spirit}</p>\n<p>6th Level: @Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.sY6TXrZoygFvnTdH]{Aspect of the Beast}</p>\n<p>10th Level: @Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.d43smTgofqUn3rNc]{Spirit Walker}</p>\n<p>14th Level: @Compendium[pergasha-foundryvtt.class-features.RHXUnTJQfREH1eIK]{Totemic Attunement}</p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"","levels":1,"subclass":"","hitDice":"d12","hitDiceUsed":0,"saves":["str","con"],"skills":{"number":2,"choices":["ani","ath","itm","nat","prc","sur"],"value":[]},"spellcasting":{"progression":"none","ability":""},"damage":{"parts":[]}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"6MjHZcsM3LMnDvhh":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.pergasha-foundryvtt.classes.pvEzGSv71zBhaolc"}},"_id":"r3Sdk1IbW6LNwAIc"}
